Paṭiccavāra
Paccayapaccanīya
Suddha
5.
2820Nahetuyā dve, naārammaṇe pañca, naadhipatiyā cha, naanantare pañca…pe…  naupanissaye pañca, napurejāte satta, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane nava, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, naāhāre ekaṃ…pe…  namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte pañca, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā pañca, novigate pañca. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
